data.description: This is an investor dream!  There is so much potential in this home for a complete remodel. There is character in this home with vaulted ceilings, older fixtures, and much more.     This is being sold AS IS WHERE IS WITH ALL FAULTS.  Seller will assume NO REPAIRS, no cleaning out, no removal of any items.  All items remaining will be on the buyers responsibility to take care of possession.   Utilities are not on.   Schedule today and get your own tour.
